<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَالجَوَازِمُ ثَمَانِيَةَ عَشَرَ؛<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهِيَ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>لَمْ، وَلَمَّا، وَأَلَمْ، وَأَلَمَّا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَلَامُ الأَمْرِ وَالدُّعَاءِ، وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«لَا»</span> فِي النَّهْيِ وَالدُّعَاءِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَإِنْ، وَمَا، وَمَنْ، وَمَهْمَا، وَإِذْمَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَأَيٌّ، وَمَتَى، وَأَيَّانَ، وَأَيْنَ، وَأَنَّى.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَحَيْثُمَا، وَكَيْفَمَا، وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«إِذَا»</span> فِي الشِّعْرِ خَاصَّةً.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>* * *<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>